{"tid":240252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩具從天降 擊傷婦人頭","createTime":"2017-05-12T09:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T11:05:11.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb8a58f8eca828e6aacd7ee16d683e3fdbca6a6","tid":240252,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>玩具從天降 擊傷婦人頭</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170512/large/1494579334_724d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170512%2Flarge%2F1494579334_724d.jpg&h=392dd79b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北角發生墮物傷人案，一名老婦行經錦屏街41A號對開時，被一件玩具由高處墮下擊傷頭部。救護員到場替傷者包紮後送院，警方正調查案件。"},{"pid":"50740d7fa641f5b324be1841e952a8cb124dbc6d","tid":240252,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"北角天降玩具車，女途人穿頭。下午3時30分，一名婦人途經錦屏街41號東發大廈對開，一輛玩具車突然從天而降，擊中婦人頭部，婦人當場頭破血流，衣衫染血，其他街坊見狀，即時致電報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕至，即場替婦人包紥，再把她送院治理。警方在場調查，追尋玩具車從何處墮下，暫時無人被捕。"},{"pid":"6d7c3bf67a88a080c30454ed5d50a185cc8fbc24","tid":240252,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"性玩具？"},{"pid":"a21da14377bdac4e1fabf63a34ead9364661b259","tid":240252,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"廢老=無限生命值"},{"pid":"e6add6c5ba04ff3283043840c90194689cd4d109","tid":240252,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2589a320501e421bb80e2fbabd8ec884d0a2f212","tid":240252,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"冇陰公 希望位阿婆早日康復啦"},{"pid":"3aa72c17e27f7af36618c8c40c152dac75087583","tid":240252,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44374427b92aca9162041c5d41765bd39bb67878",